{JUNIOR TENNIS}
The{tennis courts}are at{Wragby Town {Hall.}There are tennis lessons every Monday in the summer.The juniors go from 18_19.00h,then the seniors play afterwards.Mrs. Anstice and Mrs.Day are the coaches and,each week,some of us play a game.
There are two doors to the tennis court,both combination locked.The court is surrounded by a green wire mesh.Beside the court is the tennis pavillion.Inside that, there are the tennis balls,benches and a table.At the end of each session, we usually have a drink of orange squash.
